long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Fork/updated version of the original PoE Wiki Redirector, updated to also handle redirects for the PoE2 wiki. (Original: https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/poe-wiki-redirector/olimdjdkimlkghojdfglpjcookpbdfee)

Redirects PoE Fandom and Fextralife requests to PoE and PoE2 Wiki (respectively), as well as removes PoE Fandom and Fextralife search results from Google.

Redirects PoE Fandom (pathofexile.fandom.com) and PoE Fextralife (pathofexile2.wiki.fextralife.com) requests to PoE Wiki (poewiki.net) and PoE2 Wiki (poe2wiki.net), also adds an option to remove PoE Fandom and Fextralife search results from Google search results.
